channel.title: Sexy 289
channel.description:
[b]Client base: 289 Lookalike. Server base: Shard Revolutions.[/b]
Me and my co-partner Chris(gravenfire23) are trying to recreate what most people miss. The good old days of runescape back in 2002-2004.
To do this I am using the "Shard Revolutions" base because it has a lot of potential and it can hold much over 2000 npcs without one little bit of lagg. I will add pictures of my development throughout the project.
[u][b]Latest Updates:[/b][/u] Model Preloading.
[u][b]To do list:[/b][/u] Add all the emotes in the emote tab. Edit player vs npc. (at the moment it stands on the npc) Add all the correct weapon requirements. Edit the packets so it doesn't disconnect after a kill. Better combat.
[img]http://i44.tinypic.com/33jl6c8.png[/img]
More, coming soon!
[u][b]Contributors:[/b][/u] No contributors yet. Be the first? :)
